a most delighful movie for everyone i possibly watched hundreds of movies , and this one is surely one of the most delighful movies i have ever seen . i watched it with my dog sultan , and he loved it as much as i did . the story is interesting and amuzing , the characters simply adorable . it touches your heart , pleases your senses , and relaxes your mind . could you ask for more ? i would recommend this movie to everyone of all ages . you could see it again and again and it wo n't tire on you because there is real joy at its core . it aims to share this joy with you , and it could n't do a better job . bravo ! !